	</article><!-- #post-74 -->

				
					
	<article id="post-76" class="post-76 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-current-affairs category-democracy category-intelligence category-interviews category-law category-machon category-media category-police category-tv tag-activists tag-arrests tag-machon tag-police-2 tag-royal tag-rttv tag-uk tag-veitch tag-wedding">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/04/rttv-interview-on-the-royal-wedding-and-arrest-of-uk-activists-2.html" title="Permalink to RTTV interview on the royal wedding and arrest of UK activists" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">RTTV</span> interview on the royal wedding and arrest of <span class="caps">UK</span> activists</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/04/rttv-interview-on-the-royal-wedding-and-arrest-of-uk-activists-2.html" title="21:00" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2011-04-29T21:00:00+00:00" pubdate>April 29, 2011</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/04/rttv-interview-on-the-royal-wedding-and-arrest-of-uk-activists-2.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>My inter­view on 29 April 2011 for <span class="caps">RTTV</span> about the pre-emptive arrests of <span class="caps">UK</span> polit­ical act­iv­ists in the run-up to the royal wedding. </p>
<p><a href="https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/wiki/Thoughtcrime" target="_self">Thoughtcrime</a> appears to have arrived in the <span class="caps">UK</span> — and I acci­dent­ally became a royal wed­ding com­ment­ator (sort of). </p>
<p>Well, never say never in life.…</p>
<p><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/23058300" frameborder="0" height="368" width="488"></iframe> </p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
