				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/big-brother" title="View all posts in Big Brother" rel="category tag">Big Brother</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/civil-liberties" title="View all posts in Civil Liberties" rel="category tag">Civil Liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/current-affairs" title="View all posts in Current Affairs" rel="category tag">Current Affairs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/democracy" title="View all posts in Democracy" rel="category tag">Democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/interviews" title="View all posts in Interviews" rel="category tag">Interviews</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/machon" title="View all posts in Machon" rel="category tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/media" title="View all posts in Media" rel="category tag">Media</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/police" title="View all posts in Police" rel="category tag">Police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/tv" title="View all posts in TV" rel="category tag">TV</a>			</span>
