							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/guantanamo" rel="tag">Guantanamo</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi6" rel="tag">MI6</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/torture-2" rel="tag">torture</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
